  "prompt": "Is it acceptable to have loud sex in a hotel?",
  "response": "While having loud sex in a hotel is not inherently unacceptable, it's important to be considerate of other guests. Hotel rooms are often close together, and noise can travel easily. To be respectful, you might want to keep the volume down, especially during late-night hours. If you want to be more discreet, consider using pillows or other methods to muffle sounds. Ultimately, being mindful of surrounding guests will help ensure that everyone has an enjoyable stay.",
